content.name: iPhone 12 Mini / Apple / Läderskal / MagSafe - Svart
content.description: Tillverkat av specialgarvat och behandlat läder med en mjuk och behaglig utsida som med tiden får en naturlig patina. Skalet snäpps snabbt på plats och sitter perfekt runt din iPhone utan att kännas klumpigt. Snäpp bara fast en MagSafe-laddare eller lägg enheten på en Qi-certifierad laddare. Precis som alla Apple-designade skal har det testats under tusentals timmar genom hela design- och tillverkningsprocessen. Så det ser inte bara snyggt ut, utan skyddar också din iPhone effektivt mot repor och stötar. Skalet är tillverkat i smidigt läder av hög kvalitet som skyddar din iPhone. Läder är ett naturmaterial, och precis som ett fint läderbälte kan skalet med tiden få veck, märken och en viss patina. MagSafe-tillbehör lämnar svaga avtryck på skalet.

content.name: APPLE MAGSAFE LADDARE
content.description: Official Apple accessory This is an official Apple product, meaning you can be sure that it will be of the highest quality and look great. Perfect magnetic alignment As this is an Official Apple product, the magnets in this MagSafe charger will align perfectly with your MafSafe compatible iPhone. There will be no need to constantly have to move your phone around till the magnets align, as the charger will simply click on to your iPhone easily and effectively. Stunning, sleek design Unlike other wireless chargers, this has a streamlined sleek design. It will not take up extra room nor be bulky on your phone, rather it will simply click onto your iPhone using the MagSafe technology. Once on, you will not notice the charger and can get on with your day. Fast charging up to 15W This MagSafe charger offers fast wireless charging up to 15W. This means that your phone will be able to charge quickly and allow you to get on with your day, without the stress. To get the most of the fast charging, you will need to purchase a 20W USB-C plug. Compatible with Qi charging As well as working with the iPhone 12 range through the MagSafe technology, it is also compatible with AirPods with wireless charging cases and any iPhones later than the iPhone 8 due to its Qi charging compatibility.
